==Get the latest code==

Anonymous:
git clone https://opendaylight.org:29418/dlux.git

If you have a git account:
git clone ssh://<username>opendaylight.org:29418/dlux.git

==Install NodeJS==

For Mac, if you have brew:

* brew update
* brew install node

For Windows/Mac:

* Goto http://www.nodejs.org
* Download and install the NodeJS

Verify node is installed

$ npm --version
